00:01:39.890 --> 00:01:42.380
[Laughter]
&gt;&gt;David Oyelowo: But when I,

00:01:42.380 --> 00:01:44.760
&gt;&gt;Elijah Kelley: but you’re still black.

00:01:44.760 --> 00:01:45.760
