00:11:41.970 --> 00:11:44.910
&gt;&gt;David Oyelowo: I am so sorry.

00:11:44.910 --> 00:11:45.910
[Laughter]

00:11:45.910 --> 00:11:48.410
&gt;&gt;Andre Royo: We’ve come so far.

00:11:48.410 --> 00:11:50.420
We’ve come so far.

00:11:50.420 --> 00:11:52.920
And now we go backwards.

00:11:52.920 --> 00:11:53.920
[Laughter]

00:11:53.920 --> 00:11:58.210
&gt;&gt;Paul Snow: So these youths, if somebody
asked them in a year when did they hear about

00:11:58.210 --> 00:12:02.060
Tuskegee Airmen, they’ll have a very different
answer than what you did at the beginning

00:12:02.060 --> 00:12:03.060
of this conversation.

00:12:03.060 --> 00:12:04.110
&gt;&gt;Elijah Kelley: That’s what it’s about.

00:12:04.110 --> 00:12:09.150
I think essentially there are minorities in
the United States.

00:12:09.150 --> 00:12:17.310
Us as a culture right now, I feel like my
generation is fixated on fame.

00:12:17.310 --> 00:12:22.420
Fame without works, meaning it happens overnight.

00:12:22.420 --> 00:12:29.610
The opportunities that we’re granted, the
opportunities that Andre, David, myself, even

00:12:29.610 --> 00:12:34.380
Rick, we fought for everything that we’ve
got.

00:12:34.380 --> 00:12:41.580
And for minorities, my feeling, my vision
for these kids are to understand that these

00:12:41.580 --> 00:12:44.350
are the shoulders that you stand on.

00:12:44.350 --> 00:12:46.339
Michael Jordan, he’s amazing.

00:12:46.339 --> 00:12:50.430
Tiger Woods is amazing, LeBron James is amazing.

00:12:50.430 --> 00:12:52.190
These guys are phenomenal.

00:12:52.190 --> 00:13:00.060
But to actually see these men, to see these
modern day super heroes, I always like to

00:13:00.060 --> 00:13:06.440
say the only thing that separated them from
being Superman or Batman or Spiderman was

00:13:06.440 --> 00:13:07.440
their mortality.

00:13:07.440 --> 00:13:12.440
They went out, they fought, they saved the
world, it’s just as simple as that.

00:13:12.440 --> 00:13:19.070
And for them see that, for them to see someone
that looks like them do that, you can’t

00:13:19.070 --> 00:13:23.010
buy that type of inspiration, that’s life
long inspiration.

00:13:23.010 --> 00:13:27.540
That’s something that no one can really
verbally instill in you, that’s something

00:13:27.540 --> 00:13:28.850
that you have to see.

00:13:28.850 --> 00:13:32.820
And I think that with this movie they were
able to see that.

00:13:32.820 --> 00:13:37.190
And from what I’ve seen across the country,
and hopefully will continue to see around

00:13:37.190 --> 00:13:42.830
the world, is that kids of all colors will
get inspired to see that type of bravery.

00:13:42.830 --> 00:13:43.830
