00:14:48.360 --> 00:14:54.210
&gt;&gt;David Oyelowo: Well, I think one of the
things that drew George to wanting to make

00:14:54.210 --> 00:15:00.810
it is he recognized the universal truth in
terms of what these men did.

00:15:00.810 --> 00:15:07.600
We all face obstacles, whether it’s bullying
at school, whether it’s being a woman, whether

00:15:07.600 --> 00:15:11.410
it’s being black or any sort of minority.

00:15:11.410 --> 00:15:15.250
Or just being alive on earth today you face
obstacles.

00:15:15.250 --> 00:15:20.790
And the great thing about the story, from
a universal point of view, like I’ve said

00:15:20.790 --> 00:15:25.240
before is that they didn’t dwell on the
negative.

00:15:25.240 --> 00:15:31.899
They knew what they had, by way of talent,
they worked hard on it, and they went out

00:15:31.899 --> 00:15:35.330
and did their best every single time.

00:15:35.330 --> 00:15:43.000
And also the universal truth, there’s a
beautiful biblical quote which is, “Greater

00:15:43.000 --> 00:15:45.970
love hath no man than to lay his life down
for his friend.”

00:15:45.970 --> 00:15:53.310
And that, to me, is the definition of love,
you know, to be prepared to lay down your

00:15:53.310 --> 00:15:58.320
life for another person, for your country,
for your family.

00:15:58.320 --> 00:16:04.019
If we all had that, to some degree, within
us, you know, I am absolutely certain the

00:16:04.019 --> 00:16:06.160
world would be a better place.

00:16:06.160 --> 00:16:12.820
And that’s why so often the war years are
called the “Great Generation” or “The

00:16:12.820 --> 00:16:18.340
Finest Generation” because that was a time
where just because of the circumstances, these

00:16:18.340 --> 00:16:25.470
people had to put their lives on the line
for truth, for justice and for their countries,

00:16:25.470 --> 00:16:27.830
for the things that really mean so much.

00:16:27.830 --> 00:16:32.990
And what Elijah is alluding to, in terms of
the generation that we live in now, is that

00:16:32.990 --> 00:16:37.990
those kinds of pressures are certainly not
put on Western youth, you know, they’re

00:16:37.990 --> 00:16:38.990
not.

00:16:38.990 --> 00:16:44.769
