with our technology, with what we look like

00:16:44.769 --> 00:16:51.529
and with the idea of fame, because there isn’t
that pressure placed upon us to, you know,

00:16:51.529 --> 00:16:53.120
look out for our fellow man.

00:16:53.120 --> 00:16:59.170
So that is, I think, the universal truth within
Red Tails that I hope that anyone alive today

00:16:59.170 --> 00:17:07.030
would see, regardless of whether you’re
American or black or other race.

