00:35:20.190 --> 00:35:21.380
It’s strange right?

00:35:21.380 --> 00:35:22.380
[Laughter]

00:35:22.380 --> 00:35:24.930
&gt;&gt;David Oyelowo: What are you trying to say?

00:35:24.930 --> 00:35:26.870
&gt;&gt;Female #2: To talk like that in the movie.

00:35:26.870 --> 00:35:27.870
&gt;&gt;David Oyelowo: Oh, okay.

00:35:27.870 --> 00:35:29.170
Well, that’s a compliment, I’ll take that.

00:35:29.170 --> 00:35:32.690
&gt;&gt;Elijah Kelley: You know he thinks he’s
