00:35:37.070 --> 00:35:38.070
&gt;&gt;Elijah Kelley: See!

00:35:38.070 --> 00:35:41.080
&gt;&gt;David Oyelowo: Every time I talk to him,
“I know what you’re doin’ David, you

00:35:41.080 --> 00:35:42.080
think you’re so smart!”

00:35:42.080 --> 00:35:43.080
[Laughter]

00:35:43.080 --> 00:35:53.010
&gt;&gt;Elijah Kelley: Let me tell you, David, in
my opinion is one of the most incredible actors

00:35:53.010 --> 00:35:54.010
of our generation.

00:35:54.010 --> 00:36:02.930
It’s a testament to your, compliment, he
goes in so hard and he devotes himself at

00:36:02.930 --> 00:36:13.410
a very, very, very, very interesting and accurate
pace that I haven’t seen from a lot of people.

00:36:13.410 --> 00:36:20.790
And it’s something that a lot of people
on set learned from me, personally, and he’s

00:36:20.790 --> 00:36:24.650
one of brightest stars in my eyes, performing
on screen.

00:36:24.650 --> 00:36:32.240
I know that you guys lit up every time that
you saw Lightening and the strength that he

00:36:32.240 --> 00:36:33.240
brought to the movie.

00:36:33.240 --> 00:36:43.050
And he’s an amazing performer; you’ll
see so much more of him.

